Label: mRNA Transcript Targeted by KSRP
Comment: KSRP binds AU-rich elements in the following mRNAs: IL-8, LDLR, and NOS2 (iNOS). Binding of KSRP to the mRNA encoding Beta-catenin is inferred from mouse.

Label: NF-Y
Comment: NF-Y is a ubiquitous heterotrimeric transcription factor comprising subunits NF-Y A, NF-Y B, and NF-Y C. It binds the sequence CCAAT.
